{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":532,"text":"Let's talk dirty."},{"time":4644,"text":"A few years ago, oddly enough,"},{"time":7380,"text":"I needed the bathroom,"},{"time":10114,"text":"and I found one, a public bathroom,"},{"time":13464,"text":"and I went into the stall,"},{"time":15828,"text":"and I prepared to do what I'd done most of my life:"},{"time":19125,"text":"use the toilet, flush the toilet, forget about the toilet."},{"time":23667,"text":"And for some reason that day, instead,"},{"time":25748,"text":"I asked myself a question,"},{"time":27932,"text":"and it was, where does this stuff go?"},{"time":31808,"text":"And with that question, I found myself plunged"},{"time":35700,"text":"into the world of sanitation --"},{"time":39724,"text":"there's more coming -- (Laughter) —"},{"time":41289,"text":"sanitation, toilets and poop,"},{"time":45858,"text":"and I have yet to emerge."},{"time":48931,"text":"And that's because it's such an enraging,"},{"time":51236,"text":"yet engaging place to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54452,"text":"To go back to that toilet,"},{"time":57708,"text":"it wasn't a particularly fancy toilet,"},{"time":60502,"text":"it wasn't as nice as this one"},{"time":61937,"text":"from the World Toilet Organization."},{"time":64868,"text":"That's the other WTO. (Laughter)"},{"time":69135,"text":"But it had a lockable door, it had privacy, it had water,"},{"time":72749,"text":"it had soap so I could wash my hands,"},{"time":75013,"text":"and I did because I'm a woman, and we do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78077,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":83685,"text":"But that day, when I asked that question,"},{"time":86096,"text":"I learned something, and that was that I'd grown up thinking"},{"time":88829,"text":"that a toilet like that was my right,"},{"time":91044,"text":"when in fact it's a privilege."},{"time":94222,"text":"2.5 billion people worldwide have no adequate toilet."},{"time":99481,"text":"They don't have a bucket or a box."},{"time":103421,"text":"Forty percent of the world with no adequate toilet."},{"time":107629,"text":"And they have to do what this little boy is doing"},{"time":110126,"text":"by the side of the Mumbai Airport expressway,"},{"time":113061,"text":"which is called open defecation,"},{"time":115709,"text":"or poo-pooing in the open."},{"time":119064,"text":"And he does that every day,"},{"time":121298,"text":"and every day, probably, that guy in the picture"},{"time":123797,"text":"walks on by,"},{"time":125651,"text":"because he sees that little boy, but he doesn't see him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129109,"text":"But he should, because the problem"},{"time":131229,"text":"with all that poop lying around"},{"time":133589,"text":"is that poop carries passengers."},{"time":136597,"text":"Fifty communicable diseases like to travel in human shit."},{"time":140896,"text":"All those things, the eggs, the cysts,"},{"time":143317,"text":"the bacteria, the viruses, all those can travel"},{"time":146093,"text":"in one gram of human feces."},{"time":149501,"text":"How? Well, that little boy will not have washed his hands."},{"time":153213,"text":"He's barefoot. He'll run back into his house,"},{"time":155709,"text":"and he will contaminate his drinking water and his food"},{"time":159364,"text":"and his environment"},{"time":160768,"text":"with whatever diseases he may be carrying"},{"time":163165,"text":"by fecal particles that are on his fingers and feet."},{"time":168914,"text":"In what I call the flushed-and-plumbed world"},{"time":171186,"text":"that most of us in this room are lucky to live in,"},{"time":173813,"text":"the most common symptoms associated with those diseases,"},{"time":176862,"text":"diarrhea, is now a bit of a joke."},{"time":179688,"text":"It's the runs, the Hershey squirts, the squits."},{"time":183379,"text":"Where I come from, we call it Delhi belly,"},{"time":185229,"text":"as a legacy of empire."},{"time":187837,"text":"But if you search for a stock photo of diarrhea"},{"time":191577,"text":"in a leading photo image agency,"},{"time":194368,"text":"this is the picture that you come up with."},{"time":196388,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":198253,"text":"Still not sure about the bikini."},{"time":203432,"text":"And here's another image of diarrhea."},{"time":205928,"text":"This is Marie Saylee, nine months old."},{"time":209040,"text":"You can't see her, because she's buried"},{"time":210839,"text":"under that green grass in a little village in Liberia,"},{"time":214122,"text":"because she died in three days from diarrhea --"},{"time":217684,"text":"the Hershey squirts, the runs, a joke."},{"time":221313,"text":"And that's her dad."},{"time":223792,"text":"But she wasn't alone that day,"},{"time":225354,"text":"because 4,000 other children died of diarrhea,"},{"time":229154,"text":"and they do every day."},{"time":231824,"text":"Diarrhea is the second biggest killer of children worldwide,"},{"time":236823,"text":"and you've probably been asked to care about things"},{"time":239495,"text":"like HIV/AIDS or T.B. or measles,"},{"time":242656,"text":"but diarrhea kills more children"},{"time":244000,"text":"than all those three things put together."},{"time":247712,"text":"It's a very potent weapon of mass destruction."},{"time":252054,"text":"And the cost to the world is immense:"},{"time":255202,"text":"260 billion dollars lost every year"},{"time":257691,"text":"on the losses to poor sanitation."},{"time":260684,"text":"These are cholera beds in Haiti."},{"time":262365,"text":"You'll have heard of cholera, but we don't hear about diarrhea."},{"time":265864,"text":"It gets a fraction of the attention and funding"},{"time":268048,"text":"given to any of those other diseases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271764,"text":"But we know how to fix this."},{"time":274176,"text":"We know, because in the mid-19th century,"},{"time":277696,"text":"wonderful Victorian engineers"},{"time":280085,"text":"installed systems of sewers and wastewater treatment"},{"time":282888,"text":"and the flush toilet, and disease dropped dramatically."},{"time":287599,"text":"Child mortality dropped by the most"},{"time":289508,"text":"it had ever dropped in history."},{"time":291698,"text":"The flush toilet was voted the best medical advance"},{"time":294644,"text":"of the last 200 years by the readers of the British Medical Journal,"},{"time":297824,"text":"and they were choosing over the Pill, anesthesia,"},{"time":300667,"text":"and surgery."},{"time":302075,"text":"It's a wonderful waste disposal device."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304796,"text":"But I think that it's so good — it doesn't smell,"},{"time":308414,"text":"we can put it in our house, we can lock it behind a door —"},{"time":311193,"text":"and I think we've locked it out of conversation too."},{"time":314197,"text":"We don't have a neutral word for it."},{"time":315852,"text":"Poop's not particularly adequate."},{"time":317795,"text":"Shit offends people. Feces is too medical."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321920,"text":"Because I can't explain otherwise,"},{"time":324112,"text":"when I look at the figures, what's going on."},{"time":327680,"text":"We know how to solve diarrhea and sanitation,"},{"time":330254,"text":"but if you look at the budgets of countries,"},{"time":332584,"text":"developing and developed,"},{"time":334905,"text":"you'll think there's something wrong with the math,"},{"time":337456,"text":"because you'll expect absurdities like"},{"time":340282,"text":"Pakistan spending 47 times more on its military"},{"time":343164,"text":"than it does on water and sanitation,"},{"time":345445,"text":"even though 150,000 children die of diarrhea"},{"time":348253,"text":"in Pakistan every year."},{"time":350352,"text":"But then you look at that already minuscule"},{"time":352312,"text":"water and sanitation budget,"},{"time":354206,"text":"and 75 to 90 percent of it will go on clean water supply,"},{"time":357690,"text":"which is great; we all need water."},{"time":359643,"text":"No one's going to refuse clean water."},{"time":361950,"text":"But the humble latrine, or flush toilet,"},{"time":364901,"text":"reduces disease by twice as much"},{"time":367010,"text":"as just putting in clean water."},{"time":369434,"text":"Think about it. That little boy"},{"time":370745,"text":"who's running back into his house,"},{"time":372600,"text":"he may have a nice, clean fresh water supply,"},{"time":374710,"text":"but he's got dirty hands that he's going to contaminate his water supply with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379170,"text":"And I think that the real waste of human waste"},{"time":382674,"text":"is that we are wasting it as a resource"},{"time":385442,"text":"and as an incredible trigger for development,"},{"time":389202,"text":"because these are a few things that toilets"},{"time":391352,"text":"and poop itself can do for us."},{"time":394282,"text":"So a toilet can put a girl back in school."},{"time":397458,"text":"Twenty-five percent of girls in India drop out of school"},{"time":400290,"text":"because they have no adequate sanitation."},{"time":403808,"text":"They've been used to sitting through lessons"},{"time":405573,"text":"for years and years holding it in."},{"time":408490,"text":"We've all done that, but they do it every day,"},{"time":411250,"text":"and when they hit puberty and they start menstruating,"},{"time":413806,"text":"it just gets too much."},{"time":416149,"text":"And I understand that. Who can blame them?"},{"time":419690,"text":"So if you met an educationalist and said,"},{"time":421616,"text":"\"I can improve education attendance rates by 25 percent"},{"time":424490,"text":"with just one simple thing,\""},{"time":426688,"text":"you'd make a lot of friends in education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429501,"text":"That's not the only thing it can do for you."},{"time":432036,"text":"Poop can cook your dinner."},{"time":435096,"text":"It's got nutrients in it."},{"time":436790,"text":"We ingest nutrients. We excrete nutrients as well."},{"time":439251,"text":"We don't keep them all."},{"time":441103,"text":"In Rwanda, they are now getting"},{"time":443730,"text":"75 percent of their cooking fuel in their prison system"},{"time":446574,"text":"from the contents of prisoners' bowels."},{"time":449936,"text":"So these are a bunch of inmates in a prison in Butare."},{"time":453722,"text":"They're genocidal inmates, most of them,"},{"time":455874,"text":"and they're stirring the contents of their own latrines,"},{"time":459522,"text":"because if you put poop in a sealed environment, in a tank,"},{"time":462833,"text":"pretty much like a stomach,"},{"time":464589,"text":"then, pretty much like a stomach, it gives off gas,"},{"time":467402,"text":"and you can cook with it."},{"time":469427,"text":"And you might think it's just good karma"},{"time":471570,"text":"to see these guys stirring shit,"},{"time":474042,"text":"but it's also good economic sense,"},{"time":476342,"text":"because they're saving a million dollars a year."},{"time":478408,"text":"They're cutting down on deforestation,"},{"time":480414,"text":"and they've found a fuel supply that is inexhaustible,"},{"time":483317,"text":"infinite and free at the point of production."}]},{"cues":[{"time":488059,"text":"It's not just in the poor world that poop can save lives."},{"time":491407,"text":"Here's a woman who's about to get a dose"},{"time":493559,"text":"of the brown stuff in those syringes,"},{"time":495312,"text":"which is what you think it is,"},{"time":497248,"text":"except not quite, because it's actually donated."},{"time":500292,"text":"There is now a new career path called stool donor."},{"time":503174,"text":"It's like the new sperm donor."},{"time":504994,"text":"Because she has been suffering from a superbug called C. diff,"},{"time":507987,"text":"and it's resistant to antibiotics in many cases."},{"time":511431,"text":"She's been suffering for years."},{"time":512943,"text":"She gets a dose of healthy human feces,"},{"time":516035,"text":"and the cure rate for this procedure is 94 percent."},{"time":520516,"text":"It's astonishing, but hardly anyone is still doing it."},{"time":524914,"text":"Maybe it's the ick factor."},{"time":526936,"text":"That's okay, because there's a team of research scientists"},{"time":529806,"text":"in Canada who have now created a stool sample,"},{"time":532783,"text":"a fake stool sample which is called RePOOPulate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535567,"text":"So you'd be thinking by now, okay, the solution's simple,"},{"time":537855,"text":"we give everyone a toilet."},{"time":539740,"text":"And this is where it gets really interesting,"},{"time":541893,"text":"because it's not that simple, because we are not simple."},{"time":544818,"text":"So the really interesting, exciting work --"},{"time":548911,"text":"this is the engaging bit -- in sanitation is that"},{"time":551847,"text":"we need to understand human psychology."},{"time":554175,"text":"We need to understand software"},{"time":556551,"text":"as well as just giving someone hardware."},{"time":558903,"text":"They've found in many developing countries that"},{"time":560685,"text":"governments have gone in and given out free latrines"},{"time":563407,"text":"and gone back a few years later and found that they've"},{"time":565563,"text":"got lots of new goat sheds or temples or spare rooms"},{"time":569686,"text":"with their owners happily walking past them"},{"time":572053,"text":"and going over to the open defecating ground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":575863,"text":"So the idea is to manipulate human emotion."},{"time":578887,"text":"It's been done for decades. The soap companies did it"},{"time":581388,"text":"in the early 20th century."},{"time":583327,"text":"They tried selling soap as healthy. No one bought it."},{"time":586086,"text":"They tried selling it as sexy. Everyone bought it."},{"time":590253,"text":"In India now there's a campaign"},{"time":591608,"text":"which persuades young brides"},{"time":594154,"text":"not to marry into families that don't have a toilet."},{"time":597252,"text":"It's called \"No Loo, No I Do.\""},{"time":599920,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":602267,"text":"And in case you think that poster's just propaganda,"},{"time":604242,"text":"here's Priyanka, 23 years old."},{"time":606342,"text":"I met her last October in India,"},{"time":608463,"text":"and she grew up in a conservative environment."},{"time":611520,"text":"She grew up in a rural village in a poor area of India,"},{"time":614616,"text":"and she was engaged at 14, and then at 21 or so,"},{"time":618782,"text":"she moved into her in-law's house."},{"time":620553,"text":"And she was horrified to get there and find"},{"time":622588,"text":"that they didn't have a toilet."},{"time":623880,"text":"She'd grown up with a latrine."},{"time":625247,"text":"It was no big deal, but it was a latrine."},{"time":627201,"text":"And the first night she was there, she was told"},{"time":629224,"text":"that at 4 o'clock in the morning --"},{"time":630431,"text":"her mother-in-law got her up, told her to go outside"},{"time":633270,"text":"and go and do it in the dark in the open."},{"time":636090,"text":"And she was scared. She was scared of drunks hanging around."},{"time":638160,"text":"She was scared of snakes. She was scared of rape."},{"time":641034,"text":"After three days, she did an unthinkable thing."},{"time":643516,"text":"She left."},{"time":645256,"text":"And if you know anything about rural India,"},{"time":646841,"text":"you'll know that's an unspeakably courageous thing to do."},{"time":650319,"text":"But not just that."},{"time":651376,"text":"She got her toilet, and now she goes around"},{"time":653788,"text":"all the other villages in India"},{"time":655386,"text":"persuading other women to do the same thing."},{"time":657139,"text":"It's what I call social contagion, and it's really powerful"},{"time":660600,"text":"and really exciting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":662775,"text":"Another version of this, another village in India"},{"time":664864,"text":"near where Priyanka lives"},{"time":666861,"text":"is this village, called Lakara, and about a year ago,"},{"time":670736,"text":"it had no toilets whatsoever."},{"time":672187,"text":"Kids were dying of diarrhea and cholera."},{"time":674481,"text":"Some visitors came, using various behavioral change tricks"},{"time":678823,"text":"like putting out a plate of food and a plate of shit"},{"time":681617,"text":"and watching the flies go one to the other."},{"time":683834,"text":"Somehow, people who'd been thinking"},{"time":686401,"text":"that what they were doing was not disgusting at all"},{"time":687930,"text":"suddenly thought, \"Oops.\""},{"time":689802,"text":"Not only that, but they were ingesting their neighbors' shit."},{"time":692129,"text":"That's what really made them change their behavior."},{"time":695257,"text":"So this woman, this boy's mother"},{"time":697793,"text":"installed this latrine in a few hours."},{"time":700278,"text":"Her entire life, she'd been using the banana field behind,"},{"time":702661,"text":"but she installed the latrine in a few hours."},{"time":704229,"text":"It cost nothing. It's going to save that boy's life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":707902,"text":"So when I get despondent about the state of sanitation,"},{"time":711093,"text":"even though these are pretty exciting times"},{"time":713289,"text":"because we've got the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation"},{"time":715867,"text":"reinventing the toilet, which is great,"},{"time":717929,"text":"we've got Matt Damon going on bathroom strike,"},{"time":720483,"text":"which is great for humanity, very bad for his colon."},{"time":724218,"text":"But there are things to worry about."},{"time":725932,"text":"It's the most off-track Millennium Development Goal."},{"time":728690,"text":"It's about 50 or so years off track."},{"time":731036,"text":"We're not going to meet targets,"},{"time":732372,"text":"providing people with sanitation at this rate."},{"time":735657,"text":"So when I get sad about sanitation,"},{"time":739138,"text":"I think of Japan, because Japan 70 years ago"},{"time":742457,"text":"was a nation of people who used pit latrines"},{"time":745046,"text":"and wiped with sticks,"},{"time":747178,"text":"and now it's a nation of what are called Woshurettos,"},{"time":750505,"text":"washlet toilets."},{"time":751985,"text":"They have in-built bidet nozzles for a lovely,"},{"time":754329,"text":"hands-free cleaning experience,"},{"time":757074,"text":"and they have various other features"},{"time":759246,"text":"like a heated seat and an automatic lid-raising device"},{"time":762221,"text":"which is known as the \"marriage-saver.\""},{"time":764562,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":766018,"text":"But most importantly, what they have done in Japan,"},{"time":768423,"text":"which I find so inspirational,"},{"time":769923,"text":"is they've brought the toilet out from behind the locked door."},{"time":772487,"text":"They've made it conversational."},{"time":773988,"text":"People go out and upgrade their toilet."},{"time":777390,"text":"They talk about it. They've sanitized it."},{"time":781798,"text":"I hope that we can do that. It's not a difficult thing to do."},{"time":786278,"text":"All we really need to do"},{"time":788548,"text":"is look at this issue"},{"time":790390,"text":"as the urgent, shameful issue that it is."},{"time":794702,"text":"And don't think that it's just in the poor world that things are wrong."},{"time":797475,"text":"Our sewers are crumbling."},{"time":799639,"text":"Things are going wrong here too."},{"time":801806,"text":"The solution to all of this is pretty easy."},{"time":804705,"text":"I'm going to make your lives easy this afternoon"},{"time":806426,"text":"and just ask you to do one thing,"},{"time":808779,"text":"and that's to go out, protest,"},{"time":811855,"text":"speak about the unspeakable,"},{"time":814093,"text":"and talk shit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":815632,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":817586,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}